{
  "title": "Welcome to the Red Herring Shopping Centre",
  "transcript": "Hi, and welcome to the Red Herring Shopping Centre. This is the largest shopping centre in our town, and we have over 200 stores on seven separate floors. You'll also find our restaurants and cafes, as well as an 8-screen cinema in the centre. Red Herring is accessible, and the Metro line stops right here. You can get on Line 5 and arrive at Red Herring. You can drive here as well, and our car park can accommodate up to 4,500 vehicles. The parking fare begins at £3 per hour, and there is a regular shuttle bus service between Red Herring and the park and bus terminal, which leaves every 20 minutes. The shopping centre opens at 9 am and stays open until late. 7:30 pm from Monday to Friday. On Saturdays and Sundays it shuts at 9 pm. Thank you for listening. If you have more questions, please feel free to stay behind until the end.",
